It was the best ever meet held in Czechia. and the Benchworlds in two month shall be even better.
So IPF thanks all Czech organisers and helpers to bring that meet to such a good one.
Also my thank goes to Ivanko Barbell Company as they gave according to the negotions-contract
with the IPF two bars wih a lot of Kilos ( over 800 ) to the Czech fedration for free.
These bars with high quality allowed to be the results as good as they are now. So also to
